<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            This is a student project for managing a virtual zoo. All data is stored locally 
            and used for educational purposes only.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Collection</h2>
        <p>
            The application stores the following data:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Animal information (name, species, dietary requirements, etc.)</li>
            <li>Enclosure details (climate, habitat type, security level, size)</li>
            <li>Category classifications</li>
            <li>Zoo location information</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Purpose</h2>
        <p>
            This application is built for educational purposes as part of a C# programming course.
            All data is used solely for demonstrating the functionality of the zoo management system.
        </p>

        <h2>Technology</h2>
        <p>
            Built with ASP.NET Core MVC, Entity Framework Core, and SQL Server LocalDB.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
